modules.description: Processes template files using the Jingoo templating engine, allowing content and variables to be injected into structured text formats. Works with data types that conform to the `DATA_INJECTABLE` signature, typically records or associative structures. Useful for generating HTML, configuration files, or documentation from templates with dynamic values.
